Native DIMG Loaders status (Gilles Caulier - 2005-11-28)

Format  Read  Write  ICC   MetaData  Thumb  8bits    16bits  depency     Remarks

JPG     Done  Done   Done  Done      TODO    yes      N.A     libjpeg     Metadata are EXIF/IPTC/APP13 - ICC profil automatic or manual
PNG     Done  Done   Done  Done      N.A     yes      yes     libpng      Metadata are Embedded text - ICC profil automatic or manual
TIF     Done  Done   Done  Done      TODO    yes      yes     libtiff     Metadata are IPTC - ICC profil automatic or manual
RAW     Done  N.A    TODO  TODO      TODO    yes      yes     dcraw       RAW file formats supported by dcraw program
PPM     Done  TODO   N.A   N.A       N.A     yes      yes     none

JP2  ==> TODO
EXR  ==> TODO

Others file formats are supported only in 8 bits/color/pixel using QImage/kimgio. 
QT3.x + KDE 3.4.x support these formats :

Format   Read       Write      Remarks

PSD      yes        no         Photoshop file format
JP2      yes        yes        JPEG 2000 (libjasper)
EXR      yes        no         OpenEXR (libopenexr)
XCF      yes        no
PBM      yes        yes
PGM      yes        yes  
PPM      no         yes
TGA      yes        yes
PCX      yes        yes
BMP      yes        yes
RGB      yes        yes
XBM      yes        yes
XPM      yes        yes
EPS      yes        yes
DDS      yes        no
ICO      yes        no
MNG      yes        no
GIF      yes        no

